The UNITED STATES of America v. Walter C. JOHNSON. No. 5806. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. Sept. 21, 1936.

*1018Before EVANS and SPARKS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On consideration of the stipulation o£ counsel filed this date, it is ordered and adjudged by this court that this appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed.
